is embracing, and that’s the future that everyone here at the D
Conference is excited about.</p></blockquote><div><a  title=\"Permanent link to ‘Counting Tablets as PCs’\"  href=\"http://daringfireball.net/linked/2013/05/31/shaw-ipad-pcs\">&nbsp;★&nbsp;</a></div>" "http://blogs.technet.com/b/microsoft_blog/archive/2013/05/29/the-future-is-killer-devices-connected-to-amazing-cloud-services.aspx" (20905 14624) old 29 nil nil ((title nil "Counting Tablets as PCs") (link ((rel . "alternate") (type . "text/html") (href . "http://blogs.technet.com/b/microsoft_blog/archive/2013/05/29/the-future-is-killer-devices-connected-to-amazing-cloud-services.aspx"))) (link ((rel . "shorturl") (href . "http://df4.us/leg"))) (id nil "tag:daringfireball.net,2013:/linked//6.27736") (published nil "2013-05-31T22:32:31Z") (updated nil "2013-05-31T23:58:24Z") (author nil (name nil "John Gruber") (uri nil "http://daringfireball.net/")) (content ((type . "html") (xml:base . "http://daringfireball.net/linked/") (xml:lang . "en")) "
