    ") (title nil "★ All the Mashed Potatoes"))) ("★ Google Versus" "<p>Larry Page, <a href=\"http://thenextweb.com/google/2013/05/15/google-glass/\">on stage at I/O today</a>:</p><blockquote><p>Every story I read about Google is “us versus some other company”
